エリカ HK_PT01-1

\n< Serena >Oh... I didn't expect to find a path like
this in the forest... It's definitely
easy to walk on.

\n< Serena >With this, it looks like I'll be able to get
home earlier than planned. Thank you,
Eri...
\n< Serena >What's with that expression?

\n< Erika >Hey, hey, Serena-chan. Let's talk about
love, let's be lovebirds.
\n< Serena >What is that... sen...
\n< Erika >Do you have someone you like?
\n< Serena >You're quite stubborn... aren't you.
\n< Serena >Hmm... Ah... But if I had a fiancé...
\n< Erika >Eh?!
\n< Erika >Shh! Shushu! Shh! Shh!
\n< Serena >What is that?

\n< Erika >Hey boy! If you want to date Serena-chan,
first you'll have to defeat me!
\n< Serena >Are you planning to defeat me...

\n< Serena >Well, there's no need to worry. They're
already deceased.
\n< Erika >Eh...
\n< Erika >Um... I'm sorry... I...
\n< Serena >Hm? Ah, that's not it.

\n< Serena >They are someone I don't even know the face
of. It's not something decided by our
families.

\n< Serena >One day, I was suddenly told that I would
be engaged to someone... It was about
half a year after that.

\n< Serena >While we couldn't meet due to the distance
between us, I received news that they
passed away due to an epidemic.

\n< Serena >After all, I don't know their face or voice,
so I can't even cry.

\n< Serena >...When it comes to my love life, that's about
it.
\n< Erika >Well... um... my condolences, I guess...

\n< Serena >There's no need to worry about any troubling
wounds. But I do feel sorry for them...

\n< Serena >Yes, speaking of pity... The one who was
most troubled by his death was none
other than my own father.
\n< Erika >What about your father?

\n< Serena >Currently, in my family, there are only my sister
and I as children who can succeed the
family. We are what you would call
female heirs.

\n< Serena >Needless to say, in our country, the principle
of male primogeniture is followed.
Therefore, the current situation of my
family without any sons is... quite...
troublesome.

\n< Serena >That's why, you see, I must get married as
soon as possible and give birth to a
son.

\n< Serena >If either my sister or I can give birth to
a son while our father is still alive,
then we can smoothly pass on the family
estate from our father to that child.

\n< Serena >However, it's not like just anyone can be my
husband.

\n< Serena >If possible, someone from our relatives
and with the least amount of blood
relation.

\n< Serena >The person who met those conditions and
became my fiancé was him. My father went
through a lot of trouble in negotiating
the engagement.

\n< Serena >And just when it finally seemed to come
true, everything fell apart and the
engagement was called off.

\n< Serena >I can understand the mental burden my
father had as the head of the family.

\n< Erika >What about Serena herself? Is her family in
a difficult situation?

\n< Serena >Well... honestly, there is a sense of relief.
It's not like I'm glad he's dead, but...

\n< Serena >To suddenly become a couple with an
unfamiliar man... it's purely
terrifying.

\n< Serena >However, it is our duty to inherit the family
and leave behind our bloodline. I also
think that we must give birth to a child
no matter what.
\n< Serena >So, well... I have mixed feelings.

\n< Serena >...One thing I can say is that if I had
married him, I wouldn't be here doing
this right now.

\n< Serena >I don't intend to discuss the merits or
demerits of that matter itself, but I
want to do my best in the situation I
have been given.

\n< Serena >From my father's perspective, this would
probably be considered a ridiculous
statement.
\n< Erika >Just stay quiet at home, okay?

\n< Serena >That being said, we have an older sister in
our family.

\n< Serena >The marriage has been decided. However, the
contract regarding inheritance is facing
difficulties due to the fact that my
sister's partner is from another family.

\n< Serena >Even so, if it's my older sister, she will
ultimately be able to control the
situation.

\n< Serena >That person is far more complete than
someone like me. I am nothing more than
a spare for that person.

\n< Erika >Isn't that a terrible way to put it? The one
who would be the most saddened is our
parents!
\n< Serena >...Is that so?
\n< Erika >It's already decided, right?

\n< Erika >I ran away from home too, so I won't tell
you to go back home immediately or
anything.

\n< Erika >Hurry up and find that unicorn-chan and go
back home safely to show your parents
and older sister your lively face, okay?
\n< Erika >And then get scolded a lot!

\n< Serena >Hehe, that's right. If it can be settled with
a spanking, that would be fine.
\n< Erika >Oh! I laughed! Serena-chan laughed!

\n< Serena >...If I'm funny, I can laugh too. Was I
really that serious...?
エリカ HK_PT01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1
\n< Erika >Alright. I can see the road ahead.

\n< Erika >If we've come this far, there's no need to
worry anymore.
\n< Serena >Already...?
\n< Erika >Ah...

\n< Serena >So, you were indeed escorting me. I had a
feeling that was the case...
\n< Erika >I'm sorry... I was just worried...

\n< Serena >...Well, it's fine. I've already gotten used to
being treated like a child by you.

\n< Serena >It's true that I've been constantly relying
on others for help, even though I don't
really want to.

\n< Serena >In order to convince you, I must show you
that I can also help you.
\n< Erika >But it's not like that...

\n< Serena >Anyway, this shortcut was helpful. I'll
sincerely thank you for that.

\n< Serena >However, it's like a tunnel in the middle of the
forest. If there's something this
convenient, I wish Master would have
told me about it...

\n< Erika >No, the people in town didn't want to use
this place. Actually, it's a bit
dangerous too. That's why I came along.
\n< Serena >And what about it?

\n< Erika >This is after that Minotaur passed through
here.

\n< Erika >When I was in an excited state, in other
words, when I came to attack the town.

\n< Erika >If we pass through once, there's a
possibility we might come out again.

\n< Serena >...Idiot. This is the aftermath of just one
monster's destruction...?
※カメラ上のほうまでスクロール

\n< Erika >We might need military weapons, don't you
think?
\n< Serena >....

\n< Serena >With this, we have \V[2501] more to go until
our goal. Thanks to Erika-sama, it seems
like we can handle one more today.
\n< Serena >....
"  Thanks to Lady Erika's guidance, I was able to return home early."
"  This should allow me to handle one more job today.  Let's head to the guild."

events.name: 第一部ラストイベント　移動

parameters:
\n< Serena >...It seems like it will still take some time
to get through the forest. I hope Erika-
sama is safe...

\n< Serena >However, to help someone and end up getting
caught... It's just like Erika-sama...

\n< Serena >Come to think of it, I was saved by Lady
Erika in this forest... So, this time
it's my turn!
\n< Serena >I will definitely show you my help...!
